flowchart TB
    subgraph Browser
        SPA[SPA Client]
    end

    subgraph Backend
        BFF[BFF Server]
        Session[(Session Store)]
    end

    subgraph External
        AuthZ[Auth Server]
        API[Resource Server]
    end

    SPA -->|Session cookie| BFF
    BFF -->|OAuth flow| AuthZ
    BFF -->|Store tokens| Session
    BFF -->|Access token| API
